0x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/4.2-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/4.2-450x253.jpg 450w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/4.2-140x79.jpg 140w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/4.2.jpg 1400w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i trong ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t 2020<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>S\u1ef1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a tr\u00e0o l\u01b0u ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i &#8211; Modernism t\u1ea1i Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 20, c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 20 \u0111\u00e3 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t. Ng\u00e0y nay, phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef quen thu\u1ed9c, m\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb gia ch\u1ee7 y\u00eau th\u00edch s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n gu th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 mang \u0111\u1eadm d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/1.1-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"xu-huong-noi-that-nam-2020\" class=\"wp-image-8551\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/1.1-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/1.1-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/1.1-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/1.1-450x253.jpg 450w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/1.1-140x79.jpg 140w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/1.1.jpg 1400w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cho c\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng gian h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf. B\u1edfi n\u00f3 gi\u00fap t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a kh\u00f4ng gian, \u0111em l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c m\u1ed9t c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng l\u1edbn h\u01a1n di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u1eb5n c\u00f3. \u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1eadn d\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u00e1c d\u1ea1ng h\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u00e1o b\u1ea1o, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc trung t\u00ednh n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt, \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1ee9ng.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link\" href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/noi-that-chung-cu-imperial-minh-khai\/\" style=\"border-radius:50px\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t Imperia Minh Khai<\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>S\u1ef1 t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n trong phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc trong xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n tinh t\u1ebf. S\u1ef1 t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t, chi ti\u1ebft trang tr\u00ed, \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t v\u00e0 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n theo c\u00e1ch ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a n\u00f3.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"614\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads